TextBody:
Hey Bob,

Thank you for contacting Netwrix technical support. Which report are you looking at for the changes? It should show up under the 2-AD_Changes job, either the AD_Changes_AttributeChange_Details view or the Attribute Changes report if you're seeing it on the ExtendedAttributesPivotView.

As for the warnings on the ADI Scan, they shouldn't affect anything: https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/z-kb-articles-salesforce/page/kA0Qk0000000divKAA.html

Thank you,

Tay Caliguiri

Senior Technical Support Engineer
